title.narrative: Rural Development: Southern Region Cooperatives Development and Credit Project

description.narrative: 1. Improve the standard of living of rural households as members of service cooperatives.2. Develop service cooperatives as independent and financially viable grassroots level institutions.3. Strengthen the institutional capacity of the project implementation agencies.4. Improve access by rural households to markets, credit and improved production technologies.5. Reduce the burden of disease (BoD) and thereby increase the productivity of household labour and family incomes
